# Rider specs

Before changing rider routes or session behavior:

1. Read `docs/flows/rider-overview.md` and cross-check Notion **Screen Flows** (Rider Login & FTUE, Trip Planning, Delivery, Checkout).
2. Keep URL paths aligned with that overview unless the spec in Notion changes.
3. Dummy inventory and markets live in `src/lib/dummy-data/index.ts` — extend there for new POC scenarios.
